snippet.title: ValiDate: Struggling Singles in your Area Demo Trailer (2022)
snippet.description:
ValiDate: Struggling Singles in your Area is coming summer of 2022 but we have a new demo coming out on April 15th!

Wishlist us AND play the demo at steam.validategame.com

Follow us on Twitter for all of our most recent updates! https://twitter.com/ValiDateGame

Visit our website https://validategame.com/

Subscribe to our Patreon https://www.patreon.com/validategame
